title: Torrent Ratio Keeper Monster Classic v3.7
description:
TRK v3.7 release is the best ratio/upload increase tool for all private trackers.
* Support for uTorrent/BitTorrent/BitComet/Vuze/ABC/BitLord/Deluge torrent clients.
* Support for https trackers for uTorrent/BitTorrent/BitComet.
* Upload increase up to 1000%
* Classic Skin.

Expert features:
1. Seeder Mode: tracker will see you as seeder and not as a leecher. You can download anything without care about your ratio. I love this feature. Even without upload increase I can download anything :D
2. Network problems emulation: Tracker will not see uploading/downloading at all.
